---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy | MyCalendarTools" description="Privacy policy for MyCalendarTools covering analytics, ads, browser data, cookies, and contact details.">
  <div class="hero">
    <div class="breadcrumbs"><a href="/">Home</a> / <span>Privacy</span></div>
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>This policy explains what MyCalendarTools does with browser-detected information, analytics, ad technology, and contact submissions.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="card">
    <h2>What we use</h2>
    <p>MyCalendarTools uses standard browser capabilities like timezone detection to improve the local date experience. Ad technology may use cookies and device information to deliver and measure ads. Basic analytics may be used to understand page usage and improve the site.</p>
    <h2>What we do not require</h2>
    <p>You do not need to create an account to use the site. Tools are designed to be accessible without signups or gated access.</p>
    <h2>Third-party services</h2>
    <p>Advertising may be served by Google AdSense using publisher ID <strong>ca-pub-3257080821006753</strong>. If embedded tools, payment links, or external support links are added, those services will be governed by their own policies as well.</p>
    <h2>GDPR / CCPA style notice</h2>
    <p>If you are in a region with privacy rights, you may contact <a href="mailto:ascensiondigitalagency@outlook.com">ascensiondigitalagency@outlook.com</a> to ask a question about the information submitted through contact forms.</p>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Email: <a href="mailto:ascensiondigitalagency@outlook.com">ascensiondigitalagency@outlook.com</a></p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
